# Local OMC orchestration state. Patterns match at any depth so subagents
# spawned with cwd=<provider-dir> can't accidentally land state files in a
# committed location (M4 azure executor incident, 2026-04-28).
# Durable plan/spec artifacts under .omc/plans/ and .omc/specs/ are committed.
**/.omc/state/
**/.omc/sessions/
**/.omc/project-memory.json
**/.omc/notepad.md
**/.omc/last-tool-error.json
**/.omc/mission-state.json
**/.omc/subagent-tracking.json
**/.omc/agent-replay-*.jsonl

# Local Claude Code session state.
.claude/

# Compiled binaries from `go build .` in example modules. Each example/<name>/
# is `package main` so `go build .` from inside that dir produces a binary
# named <name>. Keeping these out of git so a routine local build doesn't
# pollute git status.
/examples/*/quickstart
/examples/quickstart/quickstart
/examples/multipart/multipart
/examples/direct_grant_qiniu/direct_grant_qiniu
/examples/direct_grant_upyun/direct_grant_upyun
/examples/streaming_write/streaming_write
# `go build ./examples/<name>` from repo root drops the binary at repo root
/quickstart
/multipart
/direct_grant_qiniu
/direct_grant_upyun
/streaming_write
.omx/
.DS_Store
